NFS Reloaded
===========

A simple car racing game in which you have to save your car from the oncoming opponents' cars.

License: GPL v3.0
Version History:
    2.0       Date: June 11, 2009, rewrite using a class
    1.0       Date: December 12, 2008, Initial code base

This was created as a school project using the historical TurboC compiler and uses headers such as graphics.h, conio.h and dos.h. Couldn't get this to compile on modern machines.
I may port this to a modern GUI toolkit sometime.
